  <div class="cf" style="background: url(/static/img/landing.jpg) no-repeat center center fixed; background-size: cover; ">
    <div class="fl pa3 bg-white black-70 measure-narrow f3 pv4">
      <header class="bb b--black-70">
        <h3 class="f2 fw7 ttu tracked lh-title mt0 mb3 avenir">
        About</h3>
      </header>
      <section class="pt2 pb4">

        <p class="f5 lh-copy measure-wide">
         Stories Incognito asks readers to write about their lives, on topics in which they are the only authority.  Topics are intentionally wide-ranging to allow room for creativity and expression.
</p>
        <p class="f5 lh-copy measure-wide">
        Stories Incognito accepts all stories, as long as they are nonfiction. The style of writing is not as important as being genuine and thoughtful. 
</p>
        <p class="f4 lh-copy measure-wide">

There is no word limit.

</p>
        <p class="f5 lh-copy measure-wide">
You may <a href="/write">submit stories online</a> or you can mail stories to ADDRESS.
</p>



      </section>
    </div>



    <div class="fl pa3 bg-white black-70 measure-narrow f3 pv2">
