        Curating</h3>
      </header>
      <section class="pt2 pb4">

        <p class="f4 lh-copy measure-wide">
         All stories are accepted.
</p>
        <p class="f5 lh-copy measure-wide">
        In order to ensure privacy of the writer, stories will be edited to remove identifying
        names, places, or occupations. Unless crucial to the story, such instances will be changed to
        pseudo-names.
</p>

      </section>
    </div>

  </div>
